# DO NOT

* modify core_sds.md
* modify schema.md
* invent schema fields
* merge multiple features carelessly
* delete retained history wrongly
* downgrade versions
* skip questions when unclear

---

# FINAL PRINCIPLES

Correctness over speed.
Versioned evolution over document rewrites.
Preserve approved history.
Use accurate timestamps.
Ask when unclear.
Change only what is needed.
Generate implementation-ready specifications.
